criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. A medical diagnosis of type 2 diabetes according to diagnostic criteria recommended by
             WHO (2006);

          2. Older than aged 60 years;

          3. Diagnosed with diabetes at least six months before the intervention;

          4. Residing in the community, able to read and communicate in Chinese;

          5. Having intact cognitive function as indicated by the Abbreviated Mental Test of score
             >=6;

          6. Having some degree of self-care deficit as indicated by the Chinese version of SDSCA
             of score <=23.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Presence of serious mental problem or terminal illness;

          2. Previously participated in similar programs;

          3. Visual or audio impaired.
